Gender Age Ethinicity Laguage
Personality
Faculty
{userType === "Mentee" ? ( <> Previous Grades Discplinary Actions ) :( <> Teaching Experience Mentoring Experience Time Availibility Per week Do you consider studnet having past displinary actions )}
) } export default UserDetailsForm const Wrapper= styled.section` color: #000; `
